title: Leaf Shape Dog Blanket
description:
Leaf shape blanket with a soft touch, let your pup lying on it or tuck them in this softness, enjoy a lazy cozy afternoon.

These cute colors and design also give your home a nice decor.

Dual usages, as a mat or a blanket
Machine Washable, stay in shape
100% cotton, soft touch
Big size for big pup
